OL,5,G1830 Reporting Scotland
OL,6,     FThe latest news and weather from
OL,7,     FBBC News Scotland. Presented by
OL,8,     FLaura Miller.
OL,9,G1930 Food Fest Scotland
OL,10,     F5/5. Edith Bowman and Colin Murray
OL,11,     Fexplore the Nairn Show to find
OL,12,     Ftips and treats among the food
OL,13,     Fstalls, including how to spot the
OL,14,     Fperfect egg and how to choose the
OL,15,     Fjuiciest berries.
OL,16,G2000 Born to Be Wild
OL,17,     F6/10. Kaniz struggles with the
OL,18,     Fintake of rescued harbour seals
OL,19,     Fwhich need to be returned to the
OL,20,     Fwild. Meanwhile, April and Juanita
OL,21,     Fsee red squirrel Kite back to a
OL,22,     Fhome in the forest.
