OL,11,     Fon her feet when an opportunity
OL,12,     Fpresents itself.
OL,13,G2230 Still Game
OL,14,     F3/6. Scottish sitcom. Romance is
OL,15,     Fin the air when Jack asks the
OL,16,     Fwoman in the charity shop out on a
OL,17,     Fdate, but Victor may end up as a
OL,18,     Fgooseberry.
